    <item>
      <title>PowerBI柱状图完成差异对比</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/powerbi/pbi_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/powerbi/pbi_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/</guid>
      <category domain="http://localhost:1313/categories/pbi/">PBI</category>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;在PowerBI里面，默认自带的原生视觉对象，是可以自由设置功能最丰富了。比如今天要演示的柱状图，就可以通过对视觉对象误差线的设置，来实现同比变化值突出显示的效果。不仅可以标记变化长度，还能够使用颜色标记增长为绿色，下降为红色，同时标记出增长变化率。这些都是在同一个视觉对象上完成的，效果如下↓&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/richbridge/imgbed@main/powerbi/PBI_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/17246574303051.gif&#34; alt=&#34;https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/richbridge/imgbed@main/powerbi/PBI_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/17246574303051.gif&#34; srcset=&#34;https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/richbridge/imgbed@main/powerbi/PBI_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/17246574303051.gif?size=small, https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/richbridge/imgbed@main/powerbi/PBI_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/17246574303051.gif?size=medium 1.5x, https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/richbridge/imgbed@main/powerbi/PBI_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/17246574303051.gif?size=large 2x&#34; data-title=&#34;https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/richbridge/imgbed@main/powerbi/PBI_histogram_completes_the_difference_comparison/17246574303051.gif&#34; style=&#34;background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;&#34; onload=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded=&#39;&#39;;&#34; onerror=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.removeAttribute(i);}&#34;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;这种可视化方式最常用的就是同期对比，或者是和目标值的对比。我们这里就使用两种常用的方法来进行制作演示，了解了思路后，可以根据实际情况做出更多的效果。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;同比变化演示&#34; class=&#34;heading-element&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;【同比变化演示】&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e5%90%8c%e6%af%94%e5%8f%98%e5%8c%96%e6%bc%94%e7%a4%ba&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/pa</description>
